title: Re: CNN shows Trump conducting ‘amazing symphony’ [video]
text:
CNN sees Trump conducting ‘amazing symphony’ during media slam-fest [video] Posted at 11:23 pm on February 16, 2017 by Doug P. Share on Facebook Share on Twitter 
In response to Donald Trump’s sustained criticism during his Thursday press conference, CNN has said they’ve emerged as strong as ever . Strong enough, anyway, to put together this video of Trump the “conductor”: Turn your sound up and watch President Donald Trump conduct an amazing symphony – er, press conference https://t.co/vvlcu7TCfI pic.twitter.com/01Aj1DhC2k 
— CNN Politics (@CNNPolitics) February 17, 2017 
Should the piece be called “Ode to ‘Fake News'”? Yeah. Kind of hard to take the whole, "but we're the only ones standing between Trump and tyranny" thing seriously when you do this stuff. https://t.co/nfPfLnDrAs 
— Drew McCoy (@_Drew_McCoy_) February 17, 2017 Hey @chucktodd , this is what is destroying Press legitimacy… https://t.co/B8zdvxtKIu 
— Lee Doren (@LDoren) February 17, 2017 News organization, reporting things like Big J journalists. https://t.co/R6b41Tj5bB 
— Ben Domenech (@bdomenech) February 17, 2017 @CNNPolitics Buzzfeed…is this you?
